 aircraft from Second World War. Beneath, you can see mountains and deserts. Above, immaculate blue sky. You can hear loud engine noises. You actually feel the speed and turns, just like a real pilot.\n\nBut wait - there are other planes on the sky and they are coming for you!", "short_description": "Overflight is an multiplayer flight simulator. Thanks to online mode, the game changes into realistic virtual reality sky battle with lots of fun and excitement. Imagine that you are sitting behind the plane's controls."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://setapp.pl/privacy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://setapp.pl/privacy/", "publisher_name": "Setapp Sp. z o.o.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://setapp.pl/overflight", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ACTION", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GAMEPAD", "TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER"], "id": "487125282776600"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 59, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "211774683040364"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "347236099259109"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2211850045752812"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2602724360044843"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "685687018558713"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1821185064650865"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1783243411981468"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "277129863238473"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "594436187866013"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "256658895567577"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "131236347563417"},